(MedAI - Rural HealthTech Project Report) Tj
T*
(Date: 2026-03-13) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Executive Summary) Tj
T*
(MedAI is a full-stack, AI-assisted rural healthcare platform that provides symptom checks,) Tj
T*
(triage guidance, online consultations, emergency workflows, and a precaution chatbot.) Tj
T*
(It is designed to be simple, low-cost, and demo-ready without paid APIs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Problem Statement) Tj
T*
(Rural healthcare faces delayed diagnosis, limited specialist access, and slow emergency) Tj
T*
(response. Patients often have to travel long distances or wait for care. MedAI aims to) Tj
T*
(reduce time-to-triage and support faster decision-making.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Provide quick symptom check and risk scoring) Tj
T*
(- Enable consultation booking with doctors) Tj
T*
(- Support emergency escalation when risk is high) Tj
T*
(- Offer precautionary guidance with a chatbot) Tj
T*
(- Keep the experience simple, multilingual, and low-bandwidth friendly) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. Solution Overview) Tj
T*
(Patient flow:) Tj
T*
(- Enter symptoms and vitals) Tj
T*
(- AI service predicts risk and likely conditions) Tj
T*
(- User receives explanation and recommendations) Tj
T*
(- For urgent cases, emergency workflow can be triggered) Tj
T*
(- For non-urgent cases, users can book a consultation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Doctor flow:) Tj
T*
(- Manage availability slots) Tj
T*
(- Review patient bookings) Tj
T*
(- Start and complete consultations) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Admin flow:) Tj
T*
(- Confirm or reject bookings) Tj
T*
(- Review payment statuses) Tj
T*
(- Monitor operational status) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. Architecture \(High Level\)) Tj
T*
(- Frontend: React UI for all roles) Tj
T*
(- Backend: Node.js + Express REST API) Tj
T*
(- AI Service: FastAPI for prediction, interpretation, explanation, chatbot) Tj
T*
(- Database: MongoDB for users, consultations, diagnoses, hospitals) Tj
T*
(- Realtime: Socket.IO for live updates) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6. Why This Architecture and Benefits) Tj
T*
(- React: modular UI, fast iteration, consistent user experience) Tj
T*
(- Node/Express: quick REST APIs, strong ecosystem, easy integration) Tj
T*
(- FastAPI: fast Python APIs, type safety, ideal for ML services) Tj
T*
(- MongoDB: flexible schema for evolving medical data) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
