(- Socket.IO: real-time updates for critical workflows) Tj
T*
(- Separated AI service: scalable and independent model updates) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. Key Modules \(What, Why, Benefits\)) Tj
T*
(7.1 Symptom Check) Tj
T*
(What: Accepts symptoms and vitals, sends to AI service, shows risk and likely conditions.) Tj
T*
(Why: Early triage helps in rural settings.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Fast decision support and clear next steps.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.2 Symptom Interpreter) Tj
T*
(What: Converts free-text into structured symptom codes.) Tj
T*
(Why: Users describe symptoms in natural language.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Works offline, predictable, no paid APIs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.3 AI Prediction Model) Tj
T*
(What: RandomForest classifier using symptoms and vitals.) Tj
T*
(Why: Robust for tabular data and interpretable.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Stable predictions with feature importance.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.4 Diagnosis Explanation) Tj
T*
(What: Generates human-readable summary and action.) Tj
T*
(Why: Raw probabilities are not enough for patients.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Builds trust and clarity.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.5 Precaution Chatbot) Tj
T*
(What: Rule-based suggestions and precautions.) Tj
T*
(Why: Immediate self-care guidance.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Safe, low-cost, deterministic responses.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.6 Consultations) Tj
T*
(What: Booking flow, payments, meetings, confirmations.) Tj
T*
(Why: Bridges AI triage with real clinical care.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: End-to-end patient journey.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.7 Emergency Workflow) Tj
T*
(What: Triggers urgent response and notifications.) Tj
T*
(Why: High-risk cases need escalation.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Faster response and clearer guidance.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7.8 Profiles) Tj
T*
(What: Role-based profile pages with edit functionality.) Tj
T*
(Why: Official and accountable identity.) Tj
T*
(Benefits: Trust and better record-keeping.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. Data Flow \(Simplified\)) Tj
T*
(- UI sends symptoms to backend) Tj
T*
(- Backend forwards to AI service) Tj
T*
(- AI returns prediction, explanation, probabilities) Tj
T*
(- Backend stores diagnosis and returns to UI) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
